{"id":569854,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/10/共青团中央-近期冒名共青团中央推特帐号有/","date":"2017-10-10T03:43:10Z","modified":"2017-10-10T03:43:10Z","title":"共青团中央 | 近期冒名“共青团中央”推特帐号有关情况综述","content":"<p>近期，境外社交网站推特（Twitter）上出现一批冒名“共青团中央”的帐号，发布了一些不符合共青团中央立场和主张的内容。</p>\n<p>共青团中央在微信公众号、微博公众号，中国青年报微信公众号，中国青年网微信公众号上再次郑重公告：</p>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<blockquote><p>共青团中央及所属机构从未在推特上以任何名义开设任何帐号。这些帐号和信息的出现，是对共青团中央名誉的损害，是对共青团中央合法权益的侵犯。希望广大网友遵守我国关于互联网管理的各项规定，不相信、不转发冒名信息。</p></blockquote>\n<p>事件梗概</p>\n<p>为了帮助广大网友认清冒名“共青团中央”的推特帐号的有关情况，我们对此次事件进行了梳理，现综述如下：</p>\n<p>9月上旬，推特上开始出现以“共青团中央”“共青团”或类似关键词为用户名的帐号，并持续增加。截至10月8日，冒名帐号多达27个。（根据推特规则，同一个用户名可以重复使用，通过用户ID进行区别）</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-13.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-569855\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-13.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"561\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-13.jpg 720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-13-294x300.jpg 294w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-13-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-2-2.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-569856\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-2-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"545\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-2-2.jpg 592w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-2-2-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-2-2-300x297.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-2-2-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>这些帐号多使用与团中央官方微博、微信相同的头像，并模仿官方口吻，有的帐号与团中央微博、微信内容同步，有的经常发布似是而非的“正面新闻”，有的“辟谣”称其他帐号虚假来自证真实，使大量国内外网民信以为真。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-3-2.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-569858\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-3-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"337\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-3-2.jpg 442w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-3-2-300x230.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-4-2.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-569860\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-4-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"465\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-4-2.jpg 439w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-4-2-284x300.jpg 284w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-5-2.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-569862\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-5-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-5-2.jpg 586w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-5-2-300x227.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p>细心的网友可能已经发现，<strong>这些帐号于9月中下旬集中注册的就有11个，并且互有互动，组织策划痕迹明显。</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-569881\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"443\" height=\"164\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640.png 443w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-300x111.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 443px) 100vw, 443px\" /></a></p>\n<p>接到网友举报后，共青团中央分别于<strong>9月15日和9月18日</strong>通过团中央官方微博进行辟谣。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-6-2.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-569864\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-6-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"358\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-6-2.jpg 598w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-6-2-300x244.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-7-2.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-569866\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-7-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"188\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-7-2.jpg 541w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-7-2-300x128.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>但这些冒名帐号并未停止，反而变本加厉，持续发布信息：</strong>有的影射或攻击党和政府的正确决策，有的歪曲嘲讽爱国爱党行为，有的恶意调侃国家领袖，有的造谣污蔑人民军队，有的甚至挑唆“港独”、分裂国家，等等。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-8-1.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-569867\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-8-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"439\" height=\"368\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-8-1.jpg 439w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-8-1-300x251.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 439px) 100vw, 439px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-9-1.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-569868\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-9-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"368\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-9-1.jpg 504w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-9-1-300x251.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-10-1.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-569869\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-10-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"498\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-10-1.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-10-1-265x300.jpg 265w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-2.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-569857\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"443\" height=\"448\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-2.png 443w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-2-297x300.png 297w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-2-70x70.png 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 443px) 100vw, 443px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-11-1.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-569870\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-11-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"442\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-11-1.jpg 442w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-11-1-300x217.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 442px) 100vw, 442px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-4.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-569861\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-4.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"441\" height=\"65\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-4.png 441w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-4-300x44.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 441px) 100vw, 441px\" /></a> <a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-3.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-569859\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"442\" height=\"93\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-3.png 442w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-3-300x63.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 442px) 100vw, 442px\" /></a> <a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-5.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-569863\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-5.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"441\" height=\"85\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-5.png 441w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-5-300x58.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 441px) 100vw, 441px\" /></a> <a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-12-1.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-569871\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-12-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"441\" height=\"90\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-12-1.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-12-1-300x61.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 441px) 100vw, 441px\" /></a></p>\n<p>虽然共青团中央已经对此事进行辟谣，但诸多境外媒体仍然置若罔闻。<strong>BBC网站9月19日发文称：“中国共产党青年组织推特帐号遭诟病”，其他网站也纷纷趁机对团中央进行构陷。</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-13-1.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-569872\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-13-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"229\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-13-1.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-13-1-300x125.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a> <a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-14.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-569873\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-14.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"187\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-14.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-14-300x102.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a> <a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-15.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-569874\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-15.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"174\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-15.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-15-300x95.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a> <a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-6.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-569865\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-6.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"131\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-6.png 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-6-300x71.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>面对持续不断的冒名信息，10月5日，团中央通过官方微博、微信及团属各新闻媒体再次发布打假公告：</p>\n<blockquote><p><strong>【公告：以“共青团中央”为名的推特帐号均为假冒</strong><strong>】</strong>近期，推特网（Twitter）上出现了一批冒用“共青团中央”发布信息的帐号。我们郑重公告：共青团中央及其所属机构没有在推特网上以任何名义开设任何帐号，冒用我单位名称及标识损害共青团中央名誉，侵犯我合法权益，我们已经启动法律程序。呼吁广大网友遵守我国关于互联网管理的各项规定，不要转发冒名信息。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-16.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-569875\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-16.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"538\" height=\"363\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-16.jpg 538w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-16-300x202.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 538px) 100vw, 538px\" /></a></p></blockquote>\n<p>随后，此次事件的组织者又集中开设了“共青团国际”“美国共青团”“上海共青团”“共青团台湾”等6个帐号。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-18.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-569877\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-18.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"232\" height=\"227\" /></a> <a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-17.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-569876\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-17.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"229\" height=\"266\" /></a> <a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-20.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-569879\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-20.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"441\" height=\"512\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-20.jpg 441w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-20-258x300.jpg 258w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 441px) 100vw, 441px\" /></a> <a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-19.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-569878\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-19.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"444\" height=\"451\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-19.jpg 444w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-19-295x300.jpg 295w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-19-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 444px) 100vw, 444px\" /></a></p>\n<p>最新进展</p>\n<p>为了维护共青团中央名誉及合法权益，我们采取了若干应对措施。截至目前，推特站方已经对@ComYouthLeague、@ccylchina等冒名“共青团中央”的帐号处以限期更名和注销帐号的惩罚。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-21.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-569880\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-21.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"339\" height=\"296\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-21.jpg 339w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/640-21-300x262.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 339px) 100vw, 339px\" /></a></p>\n<p>在此，我们要感谢包括海外留学生在内的富有正义感的广大网友的鼎力支持！</p>\n<p>团团有话说</p>\n<p>最后，我们想说，真理不会因为诋毁谩骂而黯淡，谬误也不会因为巧言令色而增辉。</p>\n<p>共青团将一如既往地在互联网上高举理想信念的旗帜，弘扬主旋律，传播正能量，和广大青少年一道，积极践行社会主义核心价值观，不断坚定“四个自信”。</p>\n<p>我们坚信，中华民族伟大复兴的中国梦终将在广大青年的接力奋斗中变为现实！</p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,20505],"tags":[10723,30806,33377,21097,8604,21038,25836,9384,24636,14666,19036]}